Invocation Name: highway sounds
des: There's no feeling like being out on the open highway. Put yourself into gear and listen to the sounds of the road as you drift away to sleep. Get started by saying, 'Alexa, open Highway Sounds,' and enjoy a 30-minute session of sound. It's an excellent feature to use during sleep, for deep relaxation, meditation practices, or to help concentrate on your tasks.
